---
// SVG icons inline
const AlertTriangleIcon = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3Z"/><path d="M12 9v4"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>`;

const TrendingDownIcon = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 17 13.5 8.5 8.5 13.5 2 7"/><polyline points="16 17 22 17 22 11"/></svg>`;

const UsersIcon = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>`;

const DollarSignIcon = `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="2" y2="22"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>`;
---

<section class="py-24 bg-[#0f0f0f] border-b border-gray-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-industrial text-white mb-16 text-center uppercase tracking-tight">
      <span class="text-red-600 mr-3">⚠</span> O Ciclo da Morte da Agência
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative">
      <!-- Connector Line (Desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[16%] right-[16%] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900 via-yellow-900 to-red-900 z-0"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-900/20 border border-green-700/50 rounded-none mb-6 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto group-hover:bg-green-900/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 text-green-500" set:html={UsersIcon} />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 text-center font-industrial uppercase">1. O Tráfego</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
          Você faz um trabalho incrível no Google/Meta Ads. O CPL está ótimo. O volume está alto. Sua parte está feita.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-8 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-600/50 transition-colors group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-900/20 border border-yellow-700/50 rounded-none mb-6 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto group-hover:bg-yellow-900/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-500" set:html={TrendingDownIcon} />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 text-center font-industrial uppercase">2. O Gargalo</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
          O comercial do cliente demora 4 horas para responder. Ou nem responde. O lead esfria e compra do concorrente.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="relative z-10 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-8 border border-red-900/30 hover:border-red-600 transition-colors group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-900/20 border border-red-700/50 rounded-none mb-6 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto group-hover:bg-red-900/30 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500" set:html={AlertTriangleIcon} />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 text-center font-industrial uppercase">3. A Culpa</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
          O cliente diz: <span class="italic text-red-400">"Esses leads são desqualificados"</span>. O ROI some. Ele te demite.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-gray-900/50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 font-medium italic">
        "Você sabe que a culpa não é do tráfego. Mas discutir com o cliente não paga boleto. A única forma de salvar o <span class="text-white font-bold not-italic">LTV</span> da sua agência é assumir o controle do processo de vendas do cliente. Mas você não tem braço para isso. <span class="text-yellow-500 font-bold not-italic bg-yellow-900/10 px-1">Eu tenho.</span>"
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

